                                    <h1 itemprop="name headline" class="article-heading">Bacteria become “genomic tape recorders”</h1>
                
                <img class="article-cover-image" itemprop="image" typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://news.mit.edu/sites/mit.edu.newsoffice/files/styles/article_cover_image_small/public/images/2014/Genomic-Tape-Recorder_0.jpg?itok=GKAyhXn3" width="228" height="152" alt="" title="" />
                <p id="article-summary"><span itemprop="description">Engineered E. coli can store long-term memories of chemical exposure, other events in their DNA.</span>

                                                   
                </p>
            </div>
